    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's in truly pristine shape\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful 'new car' feel. I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
