    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory scent with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is entirely free of sun damage or micro-scratches. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history and a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Every electronic component, switch, and sensor operates with precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
